The SmartCommunities project is structured with the following directories:

   Directory  Contents
   ---------  ----------------------------------------------------------------------
   bin        executable (bash) scripts
   classes    compiled Java class files
   external   external project dependencies, see the enclosed README file
   scenarios  configuration files and executable scripts for running various scripts
   src        Java source code

Various notes:

- This file (and the project as a whole) is very much a work in process.
- This development environment is skewed toward using Eclipse and git.
- The runtime configuration for logging is currently log4j, however, that can be changed in the future.
